{"surah":{"number":68,"name":"القلم","englishName":"Al-Qalam","englishTranslation":"The Pen","ayahCount":52},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:29.446Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"Nun. By the pen and what they inscribe,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"نٓ ۚ","english":"Nun","translit":"noon","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلْقَلَمِ","english":"By the pen","translit":"wal-qalami","root":"قلم","audio":"wbw/068_001_003.mp3"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"and what","translit":"wamā","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_001_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَسْطُرُونَ","english":"they write","translit":"yasṭurūna","root":"سطر","audio":"wbw/068_001_005.mp3"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"You are not, [O Muhammad], by the favor of your Lord, a madman.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَآ","english":"Not","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَنتَ","english":"you (are)","translit":"anta","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِنِعْمَةِ","english":"by (the) Grace","translit":"biniʿ'mati","root":"نعم"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِمَجْنُونٍۢ","english":"a madman","translit":"bimajnūnin","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And indeed, for you is a reward uninterrupted.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّ","english":"And indeed","translit":"wa-inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكَ","english":"for you","translit":"laka","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَأَجْرًا","english":"surely (is) a reward","translit":"la-ajran","root":"أجر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"غَيْرَ","english":"without","translit":"ghayra","root":"غير"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَمْنُونٍۢ","english":"end","translit":"mamnūnin","root":"منن"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And indeed, you are of a great moral character.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِنَّكَ","english":"And indeed, you","translit":"wa-innaka","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَعَلَىٰ","english":"surely (are)","translit":"laʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"خُلُقٍ","english":"(of) a moral character","translit":"khuluqin","root":"خلق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَظِيمٍۢ","english":"great","translit":"ʿaẓīmin","root":"عظم"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"So you will see and they will see","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَسَتُبْصِرُ","english":"So you will see","translit":"fasatub'ṣiru","root":"بصر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَيُبْصِرُونَ","english":"and they will see","translit":"wayub'ṣirūna","root":"بصر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"Which of you is the afflicted [by a devil].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بِأَييِّكُمُ","english":"Which of you","translit":"bi-ayyikumu","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمَفْتُونُ","english":"(is) the afflicted one","translit":"l-maftūnu","root":"فتن"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Indeed, your Lord is most knowing of who has gone astray from His way, and He is most knowing of the [rightly] guided.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبَّكَ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbaka","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"He","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","english":"(is) most knowing","translit":"aʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِمَن","english":"of (he) who","translit":"biman","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ضَلَّ","english":"has strayed","translit":"ḍalla","root":"ضلل"},{"position":7,"arabic":"عَن","english":"from","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"سَبِيلِهِۦ","english":"His way","translit":"sabīlihi","root":"سبل"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"and He","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"أَعْلَمُ","english":"(is) most knowing","translit":"aʿlamu","root":"علم"},{"position":11,"arabic":"بِٱلْمُهْتَدِينَ","english":"of the guided ones","translit":"bil-muh'tadīna","root":"هدي"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"Then do not obey the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"So (do) not","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُطِعِ","english":"obey","translit":"tuṭiʿi","root":"طوع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"the deniers","translit":"l-mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"They wish that you would soften [in your position], so they would soften [toward you].","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَدُّوا۟","english":"They wish","translit":"waddū","root":"ودد"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَوْ","english":"that","translit":"law","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تُدْهِنُ","english":"you should compromise","translit":"tud'hinu","root":"دهن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَيُدْهِنُونَ","english":"so they would compromise","translit":"fayud'hinūna","root":"دهن"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And do not obey every worthless habitual swearer","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُطِعْ","english":"obey","translit":"tuṭiʿ","root":"طوع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كُلَّ","english":"every","translit":"kulla","root":"كلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَلَّافٍۢ","english":"habitual swearer","translit":"ḥallāfin","root":"حلف"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَّهِينٍ","english":"worthless","translit":"mahīnin","root":"مهن"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"[And] scorner, going about with malicious gossip -","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَمَّازٍۢ","english":"Defamer","translit":"hammāzin","root":"همز"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مَّشَّآءٍۭ","english":"going about","translit":"mashāin","root":"مشي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِنَمِيمٍۢ","english":"with malicious gossip","translit":"binamīmin","root":"نمم"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"A preventer of good, transgressing and sinful,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَّنَّاعٍۢ","english":"A preventer","translit":"mannāʿin","root":"منع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِّلْخَيْرِ","english":"of (the) good","translit":"lil'khayri","root":"خير"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مُعْتَدٍ","english":"transgressor","translit":"muʿ'tadin","root":"عدو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَثِيمٍ","english":"sinful","translit":"athīmin","root":"أثم"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"Cruel, moreover, and an illegitimate pretender.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عُتُلٍّۭ","english":"Cruel","translit":"ʿutullin","root":"عتل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَعْدَ","english":"after","translit":"baʿda","root":"بعد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","english":"(all) that","translit":"dhālika","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"زَنِيمٍ","english":"utterly useless","translit":"zanīmin","root":"زنم"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"Because he is a possessor of wealth and children,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَن","english":"Because","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"(he) is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ذَا","english":"a possessor","translit":"dhā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَالٍۢ","english":"(of) wealth","translit":"mālin","root":"مول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَبَنِينَ","english":"and children","translit":"wabanīna","root":"بني"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"When Our verses are recited to him, he says, \"Legends of the former peoples.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِذَا","english":"When","translit":"idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُتْلَىٰ","english":"are recited","translit":"tut'lā","root":"تلو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِ","english":"to him","translit":"ʿalayhi","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ءَايَـٰتُنَا","english":"Our Verses","translit":"āyātunā","root":"أيي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"he says","translit":"qāla","root":"قول"},{"position":6,"arabic":"أَسَـٰطِيرُ","english":"Stories","translit":"asāṭīru","root":"سطر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","english":"(of) the former (people)","translit":"l-awalīna","root":"أول"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"We will brand him upon the snout.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَنَسِمُهُۥ","english":"We will brand him","translit":"sanasimuhu","root":"وسم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَى","english":"on","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْخُرْطُومِ","english":"the snout","translit":"l-khur'ṭūmi","root":"خرطم"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"Indeed, We have tried them as We tried the companions of the garden, when they swore to cut its fruit in the [early] morning","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَلَوْنَـٰهُمْ","english":"have tried them","translit":"balawnāhum","root":"بلو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَمَا","english":"as","translit":"kamā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَلَوْنَآ","english":"We tried","translit":"balawnā","root":"بلو"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَصْحَـٰبَ","english":"(the) companions","translit":"aṣḥāba","root":"صحب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْجَنَّةِ","english":"(of) the garden","translit":"l-janati","root":"جنن"},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"أَقْسَمُوا۟","english":"they swore","translit":"aqsamū","root":"قسم"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَيَصْرِمُنَّهَا","english":"to pluck its fruit","translit":"layaṣrimunnahā","root":"صرم"},{"position":10,"arabic":"مُصْبِحِينَ","english":"(in the) morning","translit":"muṣ'biḥīna","root":"صبح"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Without making exception.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَسْتَثْنُونَ","english":"making exception","translit":"yastathnūna","root":"ثني"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"So there came upon the garden an affliction from your Lord while they were asleep.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَطَافَ","english":"So there came","translit":"faṭāfa","root":"طوف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَيْهَا","english":"upon it","translit":"ʿalayhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"طَآئِفٌۭ","english":"a visitation","translit":"ṭāifun","root":"طوف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"رَّبِّكَ","english":"your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":6,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","english":"while they","translit":"wahum","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"نَآئِمُونَ","english":"were asleep","translit":"nāimūna","root":"نوم"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"And it became as though reaped.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَصْبَحَتْ","english":"So it became","translit":"fa-aṣbaḥat","root":"صبح"},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَٱلصَّرِيمِ","english":"as if reaped","translit":"kal-ṣarīmi","root":"صرم"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And they called one another at morning,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَتَنَادَوْا۟","english":"And they called one another","translit":"fatanādaw","root":"ندي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مُصْبِحِينَ","english":"(at) morning","translit":"muṣ'biḥīna","root":"صبح"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"[Saying], \"Go early to your crop if you would cut the fruit.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَنِ","english":"That","translit":"ani","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱغْدُوا۟","english":"Go early","translit":"igh'dū","root":"غدو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"حَرْثِكُمْ","english":"your crop","translit":"ḥarthikum","root":"حرث"},{"position":5,"arabic":"إِن","english":"if","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","english":"you would","translit":"kuntum","root":"كون"},{"position":7,"arabic":"صَـٰرِمِينَ","english":"pluck (the) fruit","translit":"ṣārimīna","root":"صرم"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"So they set out, while lowering their voices,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱنطَلَقُوا۟","english":"So they went","translit":"fa-inṭalaqū","root":"طلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","english":"while they","translit":"wahum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَتَخَـٰفَتُونَ","english":"lowered (their) voices","translit":"yatakhāfatūna","root":"خفت"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"[Saying], \"There will surely not enter it today upon you [any] poor person.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَن","english":"That","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"Not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَدْخُلَنَّهَا","english":"will enter it","translit":"yadkhulannahā","root":"دخل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْيَوْمَ","english":"today","translit":"l-yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُم","english":"upon you","translit":"ʿalaykum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّسْكِينٌۭ","english":"any poor person","translit":"mis'kīnun","root":"سكن"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"And they went early in determination, [assuming themselves] able.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَغَدَوْا۟","english":"And they went early","translit":"waghadaw","root":"غدو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"with","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"حَرْدٍۢ","english":"determination","translit":"ḥardin","root":"حرد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"قَـٰدِرِينَ","english":"able","translit":"qādirīna","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"But when they saw it, they said, \"Indeed, we are lost;","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","english":"But when","translit":"falammā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَأَوْهَا","english":"they saw it","translit":"ra-awhā","root":"رأي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","english":"they said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَضَآلُّونَ","english":"(are) surely lost","translit":"laḍāllūna","root":"ضلل"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"Rather, we have been deprived.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"بَلْ","english":"Nay","translit":"bal","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَحْنُ","english":"We","translit":"naḥnu","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَحْرُومُونَ","english":"(are) deprived","translit":"maḥrūmūna","root":"حرم"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"The most moderate of them said, \"Did I not say to you, 'Why do you not exalt [Allah]?' \"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","english":"Said","translit":"qāla","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَوْسَطُهُمْ","english":"(the) most moderate of them","translit":"awsaṭuhum","root":"وسط"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Did not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"أَقُل","english":"I tell","translit":"aqul","root":"قول"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَّكُمْ","english":"you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَوْلَا","english":"'Why not","translit":"lawlā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"تُسَبِّحُونَ","english":"you glorify (Allah)?'","translit":"tusabbiḥūna","root":"سبح"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"They said, \"Exalted is our Lord! Indeed, we were wrongdoers.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"They said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"سُبْحَـٰنَ","english":"Glory be","translit":"sub'ḥāna","root":"سبح"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّنَآ","english":"(to) our Lord","translit":"rabbinā","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كُنَّا","english":"[we] were","translit":"kunnā","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ظَـٰلِمِينَ","english":"wrongdoers","translit":"ẓālimīna","root":"ظلم"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"Then they approached one another, blaming each other.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَأَقْبَلَ","english":"Then approached","translit":"fa-aqbala","root":"قبل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"بَعْضُهُمْ","english":"some of them","translit":"baʿḍuhum","root":"بعض"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ʿalā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ","english":"others","translit":"baʿḍin","root":"بعض"},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَتَلَـٰوَمُونَ","english":"blaming each other","translit":"yatalāwamūna","root":"لوم"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"They said, \"O woe to us; indeed we were transgressors.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","english":"They said","translit":"qālū","root":"قول"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَـٰوَيْلَنَآ","english":"O woe to us","translit":"yāwaylanā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كُنَّا","english":"[we] were","translit":"kunnā","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"طَـٰغِينَ","english":"transgressors","translit":"ṭāghīna","root":"طغي"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"Perhaps our Lord will substitute for us [one] better than it. Indeed, we are toward our Lord desirous.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عَسَىٰ","english":"Perhaps","translit":"ʿasā","root":"عسي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبُّنَآ","english":"our Lord","translit":"rabbunā","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَن","english":"[that]","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُبْدِلَنَا","english":"will substitute for us","translit":"yub'dilanā","root":"بدل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"خَيْرًۭا","english":"a better","translit":"khayran","root":"خير"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مِّنْهَآ","english":"than it","translit":"min'hā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"إِنَّآ","english":"Indeed, we","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"رَبِّنَا","english":"our Lord","translit":"rabbinā","root":"ربب"},{"position":10,"arabic":"رَٰغِبُونَ","english":"turn devoutly","translit":"rāghibūna","root":"رغب"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"Such is the punishment [of this world]. And the punishment of the Hereafter is greater, if they only knew.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"Such","translit":"kadhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْعَذَابُ ۖ","english":"(is) the punishment","translit":"l-ʿadhābu","root":"عذب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَلَعَذَابُ","english":"And surely the punishment","translit":"walaʿadhābu","root":"عذب","audio":"wbw/068_033_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ","english":"(of) the Hereafter","translit":"l-ākhirati","root":"أخر","audio":"wbw/068_033_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"أَكْبَرُ ۚ","english":"(is) greater","translit":"akbaru","root":"كبر","audio":"wbw/068_033_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"لَوْ","english":"if","translit":"law","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_033_008.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/068_033_009.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","english":"know","translit":"yaʿlamūna","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/068_033_010.mp3"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Indeed, for the righteous with their Lord are the Gardens of Pleasure.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"for the righteous","translit":"lil'muttaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عِندَ","english":"with","translit":"ʿinda","root":"عند"},{"position":4,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","english":"their Lord","translit":"rabbihim","root":"ربب"},{"position":5,"arabic":"جَنَّـٰتِ","english":"(are) Gardens","translit":"jannāti","root":"جنن"},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلنَّعِيمِ","english":"(of) Delight","translit":"l-naʿīmi","root":"نعم"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"Then will We treat the Muslims like the criminals?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَنَجْعَلُ","english":"Then will We treat","translit":"afanajʿalu","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُسْلِمِينَ","english":"the Muslims","translit":"l-mus'limīna","root":"سلم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","english":"like the criminals","translit":"kal-muj'rimīna","root":"جرم"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"What is [the matter] with you? How do you judge?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"مَا","english":"What","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"(is) for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كَيْفَ","english":"How","translit":"kayfa","root":"كيف"},{"position":4,"arabic":"تَحْكُمُونَ","english":"(do) you judge","translit":"taḥkumūna","root":"حكم"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"Or do you have a scripture in which you learn","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"(is) for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبٌۭ","english":"a book","translit":"kitābun","root":"كتب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فِيهِ","english":"wherein","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَدْرُسُونَ","english":"you learn","translit":"tadrusūna","root":"درس"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"That indeed for you is whatever you choose?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهِ","english":"in it","translit":"fīhi","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"لَمَا","english":"what","translit":"lamā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَخَيَّرُونَ","english":"you choose","translit":"takhayyarūna","root":"خير"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"Or do you have oaths [binding] upon Us, extending until the Day of Resurrection, that indeed for you is whatever you judge?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنٌ","english":"oaths","translit":"aymānun","root":"يمن"},{"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَا","english":"from us","translit":"ʿalaynā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"بَـٰلِغَةٌ","english":"reaching","translit":"bālighatun","root":"بلغ"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"يَوْمِ","english":"(the) Day","translit":"yawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْقِيَـٰمَةِ ۙ","english":"(of) the Resurrection","translit":"l-qiyāmati","root":"قوم"},{"position":9,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_039_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_039_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"لَمَا","english":"(is) what","translit":"lamā","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_039_012.mp3"},{"position":12,"arabic":"تَحْكُمُونَ","english":"you judge","translit":"taḥkumūna","root":"حكم","audio":"wbw/068_039_013.mp3"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"Ask them which of them, for that [claim], is responsible.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"سَلْهُمْ","english":"Ask them","translit":"salhum","root":"سأل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَيُّهُم","english":"which of them","translit":"ayyuhum","root":"أيي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِذَٰلِكَ","english":"for that","translit":"bidhālika","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"زَعِيمٌ","english":"(is) responsible","translit":"zaʿīmun","root":"زعم"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"Or do they have partners? Then let them bring their partners, if they should be truthful.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"(are) for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"شُرَكَآءُ","english":"partners","translit":"shurakāu","root":"شرك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَلْيَأْتُوا۟","english":"Then let them bring","translit":"falyatū","root":"أتي"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِشُرَكَآئِهِمْ","english":"their partners","translit":"bishurakāihim","root":"شرك"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِن","english":"if","translit":"in","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they are","translit":"kānū","root":"كون"},{"position":8,"arabic":"صَـٰدِقِينَ","english":"truthful","translit":"ṣādiqīna","root":"صدق"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"The Day the shin will be uncovered and they are invited to prostration but the disbelievers will not be able,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"يَوْمَ","english":"(The) Day","translit":"yawma","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُكْشَفُ","english":"will be uncovered","translit":"yuk'shafu","root":"كشف"},{"position":3,"arabic":"عَن","english":"from","translit":"ʿan","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"سَاقٍۢ","english":"the shin","translit":"sāqin","root":"سوق"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَيُدْعَوْنَ","english":"and they will be called","translit":"wayud'ʿawna","root":"دعو"},{"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","english":"prostrate","translit":"l-sujūdi","root":"سجد"},{"position":8,"arabic":"فَلَا","english":"but not","translit":"falā","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"يَسْتَطِيعُونَ","english":"they will be able","translit":"yastaṭīʿūna","root":"طوع"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"Their eyes humbled, humiliation will cover them. And they used to be invited to prostration while they were sound.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"خَـٰشِعَةً","english":"Humbled","translit":"khāshiʿatan","root":"خشع"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَبْصَـٰرُهُمْ","english":"their eyes","translit":"abṣāruhum","root":"بصر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَرْهَقُهُمْ","english":"will cover them","translit":"tarhaquhum","root":"رهق"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِلَّةٌۭ ۖ","english":"humiliation","translit":"dhillatun","root":"ذلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَقَدْ","english":"And indeed","translit":"waqad","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_043_006.mp3"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَانُوا۟","english":"they were","translit":"kānū","root":"كون","audio":"wbw/068_043_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"يُدْعَوْنَ","english":"called","translit":"yud'ʿawna","root":"دعو","audio":"wbw/068_043_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِلَى","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_043_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلسُّجُودِ","english":"prostrate","translit":"l-sujūdi","root":"سجد","audio":"wbw/068_043_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَهُمْ","english":"while they","translit":"wahum","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_043_011.mp3"},{"position":11,"arabic":"سَـٰلِمُونَ","english":"(were) sound","translit":"sālimūna","root":"سلم","audio":"wbw/068_043_012.mp3"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"So leave Me, [O Muhammad], with [the matter of] whoever denies the Qur'an. We will progressively lead them [to punishment] from where they do not know.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَذَرْنِى","english":"So leave Me","translit":"fadharnī","root":"وذر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَمَن","english":"and whoever","translit":"waman","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يُكَذِّبُ","english":"denies","translit":"yukadhibu","root":"كذب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِهَـٰذَا","english":"this","translit":"bihādhā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْحَدِيثِ ۖ","english":"Statement","translit":"l-ḥadīthi","root":"حدث"},{"position":6,"arabic":"سَنَسْتَدْرِجُهُم","english":"We will progressively lead them","translit":"sanastadrijuhum","root":"درج","audio":"wbw/068_044_007.mp3"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مِّنْ","english":"from","translit":"min","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_044_008.mp3"},{"position":8,"arabic":"حَيْثُ","english":"where","translit":"ḥaythu","root":"حيث","audio":"wbw/068_044_009.mp3"},{"position":9,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_044_010.mp3"},{"position":10,"arabic":"يَعْلَمُونَ","english":"they know","translit":"yaʿlamūna","root":"علم","audio":"wbw/068_044_011.mp3"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"And I will give them time. Indeed, My plan is firm.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَأُمْلِى","english":"And I will give respite","translit":"wa-um'lī","root":"ملو"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لَهُمْ ۚ","english":"to them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":"","audio":"wbw/068_045_004.mp3"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَيْدِى","english":"My plan","translit":"kaydī","root":"كيد","audio":"wbw/068_045_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَتِينٌ","english":"(is) firm","translit":"matīnun","root":"متن","audio":"wbw/068_045_006.mp3"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"Or do you ask of them a payment, so they are by debt burdened down?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَسْـَٔلُهُمْ","english":"you ask them","translit":"tasaluhum","root":"سأل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أَجْرًۭا","english":"a payment","translit":"ajran","root":"أجر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَهُم","english":"so they","translit":"fahum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّغْرَمٍۢ","english":"(the) debt","translit":"maghramin","root":"غرم"},{"position":7,"arabic":"مُّثْقَلُونَ","english":"(are) burdened","translit":"muth'qalūna","root":"ثقل"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"Or have they [knowledge of] the unseen, so they write [it] down?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَمْ","english":"Or","translit":"am","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"عِندَهُمُ","english":"(is) with them","translit":"ʿindahumu","root":"عند"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْبُ","english":"the unseen","translit":"l-ghaybu","root":"غيب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَهُمْ","english":"so they","translit":"fahum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"يَكْتُبُونَ","english":"write it","translit":"yaktubūna","root":"كتب"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"Then be patient for the decision of your Lord, [O Muhammad], and be not like the companion of the fish when he called out while he was distressed.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱصْبِرْ","english":"So be patient","translit":"fa-iṣ'bir","root":"صبر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"لِحُكْمِ","english":"for (the) decision","translit":"liḥuk'mi","root":"حكم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَبِّكَ","english":"(of) your Lord","translit":"rabbika","root":"ربب"},{"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and (do) not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"تَكُن","english":"be","translit":"takun","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"كَصَاحِبِ","english":"like (the) companion","translit":"kaṣāḥibi","root":"صحب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"ٱلْحُوتِ","english":"(of) the fish","translit":"l-ḥūti","root":"حوت"},{"position":8,"arabic":"إِذْ","english":"when","translit":"idh","root":""},{"position":9,"arabic":"نَادَىٰ","english":"he called out","translit":"nādā","root":"ندي"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"while he","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":11,"arabic":"مَكْظُومٌۭ","english":"(was) distressed","translit":"makẓūmun","root":"كظم"}]},{"number":49,"translation":"If not that a favor from his Lord overtook him, he would have been thrown onto the naked shore while he was censured.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّوْلَآ","english":"If not","translit":"lawlā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَن","english":"that","translit":"an","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"تَدَٰرَكَهُۥ","english":"overtook him","translit":"tadārakahu","root":"درك"},{"position":4,"arabic":"نِعْمَةٌۭ","english":"a Favor","translit":"niʿ'matun","root":"نعم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"رَّبِّهِۦ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbihi","root":"ربب"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَنُبِذَ","english":"surely he would have been thrown","translit":"lanubidha","root":"نبذ"},{"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلْعَرَآءِ","english":"onto (the) naked shore","translit":"bil-ʿarāi","root":"عري"},{"position":9,"arabic":"وَهُوَ","english":"while he","translit":"wahuwa","root":""},{"position":10,"arabic":"مَذْمُومٌۭ","english":"(was) blamed","translit":"madhmūmun","root":"ذمم"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"And his Lord chose him and made him of the righteous.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱجْتَبَـٰهُ","english":"But chose him","translit":"fa-ij'tabāhu","root":"جبي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"رَبُّهُۥ","english":"his Lord","translit":"rabbuhu","root":"ربب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فَجَعَلَهُۥ","english":"and made him","translit":"fajaʿalahu","root":"جعل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"of","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلصَّـٰلِحِينَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-ṣāliḥīna","root":"صلح"}]},{"number":51,"translation":"And indeed, those who disbelieve would almost make you slip with their eyes when they hear the message, and they say, \"Indeed, he is mad.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِن","english":"And indeed","translit":"wa-in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَكَادُ","english":"would almost","translit":"yakādu","root":"كود"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","english":"those who","translit":"alladhīna","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَفَرُوا۟","english":"disbelieve","translit":"kafarū","root":"كفر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَيُزْلِقُونَكَ","english":"surely make you slip","translit":"layuz'liqūnaka","root":"زلق"},{"position":6,"arabic":"بِأَبْصَـٰرِهِمْ","english":"with their look","translit":"bi-abṣārihim","root":"بصر"},{"position":7,"arabic":"لَمَّا","english":"when","translit":"lammā","root":""},{"position":8,"arabic":"سَمِعُوا۟","english":"they hear","translit":"samiʿū","root":"سمع"},{"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلذِّكْرَ","english":"the Message","translit":"l-dhik'ra","root":"ذكر"},{"position":10,"arabic":"وَيَقُولُونَ","english":"and they say","translit":"wayaqūlūna","root":"قول"},{"position":11,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","english":"Indeed, he","translit":"innahu","root":""},{"position":12,"arabic":"لَمَجْنُونٌۭ","english":"(is) surely mad","translit":"lamajnūnun","root":"جنن"}]},{"number":52,"translation":"But it is not except a reminder to the worlds.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","english":"And not","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"هُوَ","english":"it (is)","translit":"huwa","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَّا","english":"but","translit":"illā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِكْرٌۭ","english":"a Reminder","translit":"dhik'run","root":"ذكر"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لِّلْعَـٰلَمِينَ","english":"to the worlds","translit":"lil'ʿālamīna","root":"علم"}]}]}
